Subject: [PATCH 05/25] Add crawl URL state tracking for checkpoint/resume

- Add migration to create archon_crawl_url_state table
- Track per-URL status: pending, fetched, embedded, failed
- Support retry logic with configurable max_retries
- Add CrawlUrlStateService with methods for state management

This is the infrastructure for Phase 1 of ADR-001, enabling
resumable crawls after interruption.
---
