From 70d4db792584c77bf01465d6f1f00a016849eb85 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Zebastjan Johanzen <zebastian.johanzen@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 22 Feb 2026 03:57:53 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 10/25] Implement checkpoint/resume and provenance tracking
 backend

- Add checkpoint/resume filtering to crawling service (skip already-embedded URLs)
- Add provenance tracking to source management (embedding model, provider,
  dimensions, vectorizer settings, summarization model, timestamps)
- Add migration 013_add_provenance_tracking.sql to add provenance columns
- Update document storage operations to capture and store provenance
- Update recursive crawling strategy to support resume

All changes pass existing tests.
