From: Zebastjan Johanzen <zebastian.johanzen@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 22 Feb 2026 19:49:03 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 20/25] Add roadmap document outlining project direction

- Current focus: robust ingestion pipeline
- Near-term: batch processing + agent skills
- Mid-term: git + IPFS integration
- Long-term: database abstraction + knowledge graph
